highlights.text: “Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 309 weeks straight.
“One Kiss (with Dua Lipa)” by Calvin Harris and Dua Lipa is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 112 spots at #81.
Bad Bunny has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “La Jumpa” is the highest at #9.
“Bebe Dame” by Fuerza Regida and Grupo Frontera is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #59.
